Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:24.82,TITLE1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\pos(460,490)}变幻之音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是 这可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气真的是阴沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从他妹妹的学校回来后就一直那个死样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和巴斯卡比鲁之民相遇就受这么大震惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像原因在于埃利奥特·奈特雷伊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个沸点很低的少爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也在同一个学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是有缘 他和他的仆人正好救了奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我想知道关于那首曲子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都好 能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个演奏的啊 我就是那时听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那曲子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我创作的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为蕾西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啊你 有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 该把名字告诉我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道怎么称呼你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:02:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从他对艾妲的那种态度来看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是因为两家族不和的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他知道我是贝萨流士家族的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是会被排斥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对这家伙不能说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 我的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔 你这家伙 稍微看看气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少啰嗦 我倒大霉了你知不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也遇上麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然被大群学校里的女生围住 听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么真令人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也在这个学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是想不到啊 会在这里遇见你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近怎么样 过的还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你这家伙在这里 基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃利奥特 你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这装扮是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十四岁了还穿着学生制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不知羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他动粗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是你我也不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹·贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝萨流士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是奥兹不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 不是听说奥兹·贝萨流士在十年前已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃利奥特 我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 我会相信你们说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是结果呢 什么也没说就道别了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔巴特是被义弟完全拒绝所以才那么沮丧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:39.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有剩下的一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝小姐 为什么这么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是和往常一样吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还和往常一样是个没用的大胃王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请闭嘴 布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 爱丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么烦恼的事情就尽管和我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了没什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[动物对危险查知的本能]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹大人他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不理你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 我可没那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是 最近那家伙太没作为仆人的自觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前阵子抛下我不管去和小丑喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着妹妹嘿嘿地傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天因为一个莫名其妙的家伙而闷闷不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 那家伙明明是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么老是想着其他家伙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了{\fe77\fs56\fnComic Sans MS}♡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 爱丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是少女啊 太可爱了{\fe77\fs56\fnComic Sans MS}♡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是心动啊{\fe77\fs56\fnComic Sans MS}♡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 爱丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种感情就是所谓的嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  好吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 真要这么说的话 听说是又酸又甜的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并怎么不喜欢酸的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 爱丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种酸甜对于罗曼来说是必不可少的{\fe77\fs56\fnComic Sans MS}♡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗曼是什么 好吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是非常甜美的东西哦{\fe77\fs56\fnComic Sans MS}♡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐进入少女模式了啊 那我就先行告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等 布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须成为爱丽丝小姐的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不需要你们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 我以前就这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝小姐从来不叫我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 现在试着叫我「夏萝姐姐」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要叫姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意细节嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请 快 点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[动物对危险查知的本能2]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 夏 夏萝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了没 布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像收了个妹妹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么看 都只是个想要调戏年轻人的欧巴桑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 爱丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来学习罗曼的知识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐我会温柔地教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些书是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗曼的圣经哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如这本小说的这一节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没出息的哭像明明应该只能让身为主人的我看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对这种对谁都摇尾乞怜的劣犬惩罚是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和现在的我一模一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙后来怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 夏萝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 爱丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人公为了得到他的心而利用一切权利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把情敌们逐个消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 结果就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 为什么合上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这种事对爱丽丝来说还太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是接吻 我和奥兹已经做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是只披着兔皮的大灰狼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违法契约者只要得到灵体的血就可以完成契约了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是签订契约那时的事 您应该早说清楚的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有那个机会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我又不是兔子 爱丽丝才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KISS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯卡叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是以偷取女学生制服的嫌疑被抓的变态嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真敢说啊 扎克席兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被小姐们用蔑视的眼光看着也是很不错的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个M（受虐狂）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带果汁回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这次还是不知道爱妲的心上人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之全员平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来开个Party吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快快 大家都过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 祝大家平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么看 这液体都不像果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不过就是加了酒精的果汁而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世间一般把那称为酒啊 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要介意这红色的液体了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且反正你也25岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1cFFFFFF\fs60\pos(235,260)}人\N偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[也许看着不像但也20多岁]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[只是个灵体]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b0\1cA04650\fs43\bord0\fn黑体\pos(460,450)}没有未成年人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 奥兹都25岁了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分哦 叔叔 你在叹什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 爱丽丝醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}[替身]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不可以了 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[正在观赏此片的各位 请千万不要模仿]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 她已经完全醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏萝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏萝你也帮帮忙嘛 爱丽丝她醉了 在乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要拜托我的话就跪下来求我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些猪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王大人降临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是海藻头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛已经完全迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔从以前就不太能喝酒喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}[基尔巴特大人 那个是花瓶]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是 总是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}[呃 为什么对我]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是嘲笑我是海藻头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是很在意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海藻头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}海藻头是很伟大的 比那些白痴强多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒品真差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知不知道啊 笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你在说谁是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}[这边也]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不懂吗 这都听不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不懂 完全听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 谁是笨蛋 你给我好好解释一下你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看你都是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封印被解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醉到变身了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.15,0:14:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个眼红的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别和我的仆人卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.06,0:14:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 这家伙可不是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我重要的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹是我的所有物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}[责任转嫁]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你的错笨蛋兔子 把你关在马棚里让你寂寞而死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千错万错都怪你先对我的仆人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得很吵起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 奥兹争夺战又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛啊 谁来救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏萝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥 兹 大 人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我救了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}[血统原因吗]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说的话埃利奥特君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都倒下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是呢 我也觉得有点困了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那么说布雷克你其实完全没醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真是个不可爱的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.05,0:16:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到你的夸奖 我很光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为什么你要刻意装醉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不那么做的话就会那边破坏气氛了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外啊 这个世上布雷克也会看气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我揍扁你哦 奥兹君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得酒量大很帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不是什么太好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么想醉都醉不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定那是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想着「还不能死」经常这么神经紧张导致的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么正经的奥兹让我有点恶心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准侮辱我的主人 布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再来胡搅蛮缠了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.08,0:18:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁胡搅蛮缠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想对您说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请更加珍惜自己一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会很伤心 很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一醉就哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太没用了 真是一点都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下 我 那个 那个 用哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要趁此机会再换下自称呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾啊偶啊小基尔之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克 别说了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 基尔 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超令人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都让你背负着很沉重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从今以后 我自己也会努力背负的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到不用再依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 我要从了解开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是自己的事 还是大家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 下次告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于你的事 奈特雷伊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这10年所发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过变得可爱起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你也可以少操劳一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要讨厌埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很清楚并不是你做了什么不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃利奥特他是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头脑聪明但是个性很白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会 奥兹·贝萨流士君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会 里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会 埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 一定还有再次相遇的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了到那时不再被斥责
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了可以挺起胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要以我的方式前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多事想对那家伙说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是对这支曲子 还有很多想问
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好觉悟吧 埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有点头晕而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做噩梦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那个梦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建筑物在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们在死去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身处血泊之中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的剑被那些人的血染得鲜红
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再做这种梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:42.13,预告,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,280)}知识就是力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.46,0:23:45.76,预告,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,280)}我的名字叫爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:49.09,预告,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,280)}这是...什么噩梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:53.14,预告,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,280)}不要调查我的过去 巴鲁玛公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.47,0:23:57.06,预告,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,280)}有时候了解事情也会产生恐惧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.39,0:24:00.36,预告,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,280)}首先我要看的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.69,0:24:04.40,预告,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,280)}拿出汝为凯宾·辛克莱特的证据
